ingredientsDesc: IMMULITE HBsAg Confirmatory Kit HBsAg Confirmatory Assay Reagent 1 (LCH1) (Blocking Reagent): One amber glass vial (1.2 mL) of polyclonal goat antibody against HBsAg in a protein-based buffer, with <0.1 g/dL sodium azide.HBsAg Confirmatory Assay Reagent 2 (LCH2) (Control Reagent): One amber glass vial (1.2 mL) of a protein-based buffer, with <0.1 g/dL sodium azide.HBsAg Confirmatory Assay Sample Diluent (LCHZ4): Two bottles (100 mL each) of protein-based buffer, with <0.1 g/dL sodium azide. HBsAg Positive Control (LHBC3): One amber glass vial (8 mL) of human serum with inactivated ad and ay hepatitis B viral antigens, with <0.1 g/dL sodium azide.

HBsAg Controls (LHBC1, LHBC2, LHBC3)Three vials (Negative, Low Positive and Positive) containing 8 mL each. LHBC1(Negative Control): human serum without HBsAg, with preservative. LHBC2, LHBC3 (Low Positive Control, Positive Control): human serum with inactivated HBsAg, with preservative.LKHB1: 1 set. LKHB5: 2 sets.

IMMULITE HBsAgHBsAg Test Units (LHB1)Each barcode-labeled unit contains one bead coated with murine monoclonal anti-HBs.LKHB1: 100 units. LKHB5: 500 units.HBsAg Reagent Wedges (LHBA, LHBB)LHBA: 7.5 mL of a protein-based buffer, with preservative.LHBB: 7.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-HBs in buffer, with preservative. LKHB1: 1 set. LKHB5: 5 setsHBsAg Adjustor (LHBR) 4 mL of human serum with inactivated HBsAg, with preservative LKHB1: 1 vial.LKHB5: 2 vials.
